<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>新闻资讯 | 成都修茈科技有限公司</title>
  <meta name="description" content="修茈科技新闻资讯与行业观察：企业 AI 自动化、单据处理、Agent 趋势与中小企业数字化。" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="./styles.css?v={{ cssQuery }}" />
</head>
<body>
{% set activeNav = 'news' %}
{% include "partials/header.njk" %}
<main>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container page-hero-inner">
      <div>
        <span class="eyebrow">News</span>
        <h1>新闻资讯</h1>
        <p>记录修茈科技的产品动态、公司公告与对 AI 自动化、Agent 与职场协作的行业观察。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="page-hero-side">
        <p>资讯列表在构建时从数据文件生成，便于统一维护与审阅；更新流程见站内编辑说明。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid grid-3">
        {% for item in newsItems %}
        <article class="news-card reveal" {% if loop.index0 > 0 %}data-delay="{{ (loop.index0 % 3) * 80 }}"{% endif %}>
          <span class="news-label">{{ item.category }}</span>
          <h3>{{ item.title }}</h3>
          <p>{{ item.summary }}</p>
          {% if item.date %}
          <p class="footer-meta">{{ item.date }}</p>
          {% endif %}
        </article>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
<footer class="site-footer">
  <div class="container footer-inner">
    <div>
      <a class="brand-mark" href="/index.html"><span class="brand-seal"><img src="/assets/xiu-ci-logo.png" alt="修茈科技 Logo" /></span><span class="brand-name"><strong>成都修茈科技有限公司</strong><span>XCAGI Automation</span></span></a>
      <p class="footer-copy">&copy; <span id="year"></span> 成都修茈科技有限公司 保留所有权利。</p>
      <p class="footer-meta footer-legal"><a href="https://beian.miit.gov.cn/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">蜀ICP备2026014056号-1</a></p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-links">
      <a href="/about.html">关于修茈</a><a href="/services.html">产品中心</a><a href="/cases.html">客户案例</a><a href="/news.html">新闻资讯</a><a href="/developer.html">开发者门户</a><a href="/honors.html">资质与能力</a><a href="/contact.html">联系我们</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
<button id="back-to-top" class="back-to-top" aria-label="回到顶部"></button>
<script src="./main.js?v={{ cssQuery }}"></script>
{% include "partials/corp-butler.njk" %}
</body>
</html>
